            <p>Tourist attractions in America next is one of the seven wonders in the world, which is called the Grand Canyon. A great canyon that
                formed by the Colorado River, and has a geological age of 5-6 million years. For those of you who want to arrive at this tourist attraction, there are 2 transportation options. Among them:
                helicopters and jeeps. If using a helicopter, tourists will easily reach the top of the canyon, but the price is expensive. The difference with using a jeep,
                the tourists will only enjoy under the canyon only.
            </p>
            
